ed to the scoreboard. After the programme, verification confirmed that Portugal should only have received six points, leaving the total Portuguese score reduced by four points to 64.}}\n|-\n!{{Escyr|1980}}\n|[[Jos\u00e9 Cid]]\n|Portuguese\n|\"[[Um grande, grande amor]]\"\n|align=center|7\n|align=center|71\n|-\n!{{Escyr|1981}}\n|[[Carlos Pai\u00e3o]]\n|Portuguese\n|\"[[Playback (song)|Playback]]\"\n|align=center|18\n|align=center|9\n|-\n!{{Escyr|1982}}\n|[[Doce]]\n|Portuguese\n|\"[[Bem bom]]\"\n|align=center|13\n|align=center|32\n|-\n!{{Escyr|1983}}\n|[[Armando Gama]]\n|Portuguese\n|\"[[Esta balada que te dou]]\"\n|align=center|13\n|align=center|33\n|-\n!{{Escyr|1984}}\n|[[Maria Guinot]]\n|Portuguese\n|\"[[Sil\u00eancio e tanta gente]]\"\n|align=center|11\n|align=center|38\n|-\n!{{Escyr|1985}}\n|[[Adelaide Ferreira]]\n|Portuguese\n|\"[[Penso em ti, eu sei]]\"\n|align=center|18\n|align=center|9\n|-\n!{{Escyr|1986}}\n|[[Dora (singer)|Dora]]\n|Portuguese\n|\"[[N\u00e3o sejas mau para mim]]\"\n|align=center|14\n|align=center|28\n|-\n!{{Escyr|1987}}\n|[[Nevada (Portuguese band)|Nevada]]\n|Portuguese\n|\"[[Neste barco \u00e0 vela]]\"\n|align=center|18\n|align=center|15\n|-\n!{{Escyr|1988}}\n|[[Dora (singer)|Dora]]\n|Portuguese\n|\"[[Voltarei]]\"\n|align=center|18\n|align=center|5\n|-\n!{{Escyr|1989}}\n|[[Da Vinci (band)|Da Vinci]]\n|Portuguese\n|\"[[Conquistador (Da Vinci song)|Conquistador]]\"\n|align=center|16\n|align=center|39\n|-\n!{{Escyr|1990}}\n|[[Nucha (singer)|Nucha]]\n|Portuguese\n|\"[[H\u00e1 sempre algu\u00e9m]]\"\n|align=center|20\n|align=center|9\n|-\n!{{Escyr|1991}}\n|[[Dulce Pontes]]\n|Portuguese\n|\"[[Lusitana paix\u00e3o]]\"\n|align=center|8\n|align=center|62\n|-\n!{{Escyr|1992}}\n|[[Dina (singer)|Dina]]\n|Portuguese\n|\"[[Amor d'\u00e1gua fresca]]\"\n|align=center|17\n|align=center|26\n|-\n!{{Escyr|1993}}\n|[[Anabela Braz Pires|Anabela]]\n|Portuguese\n|\"[[A cidade (at\u00e9 ser dia)]]\"\n|align=center|10\n|align=center|60\n|colspan=\"2\" data-sort-value