ains phrases in [[English language|English]], [[French language|French]] and [[Spanish language|Spanish]].}}\n|\"[[Dan\u00e7a comigo (Vem ser feliz)|Dan\u00e7a comigo]]\"\n|align=center|11\n|align=center|88\n|-\n!{{Escyr|2008}}\n|[[V\u00e2nia Fernandes]]\n|Portuguese\n|\"[[Senhora do mar (Negras \u00e1guas)]]\"\n|align=center|13\n|align=center|69 \n|align=center bgcolor=\"silver\"|2\n|align=center bgcolor=\"silver\"|120\n|-\n!{{Escyr|2009}}\n|[[Flor-de-Lis]]\n|Portuguese\n|\"[[Todas as ruas do amor]]\"\n|align=center|15\n|align=center|57\n|align=center|8\n|align=center|70\n|-\n!{{Escyr|2010}}\n|[[Filipa Azevedo]]\n|Portuguese\n|\"[[H\u00e1 dias assim]]\"\n|align=center|18\n|align=center|43\n|align=center|4\n|align=center|89\n|-\n!{{Escyr|2011}}\n|[[Homens da Luta]]\n|Portuguese\n|\"[[A luta \u00e9 alegria]]\"\n|colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"2\" {{N/A|Failed to qualify}}\n|align=center|18\n|align=center|22\n|-\n!{{Escyr|2012}}\n|[[Filipa Sousa]]\n|Portuguese\n|\"[[Vida minha]]\"\n|align=center|13\n|align=center|39\n|-\n|{{N/A|{{Escyr|2013}}}}\n|colspan=\"7\" {{N/A|Did not participate}}\n|-\n!{{Escyr|2014}}\n|[[Suzy (singer)|Suzy]]\n|Portuguese\n|\"[[Quero ser tua]]\"\n|colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"2\" {{N/A|Failed to qualify}}\n|align=center|11\n|align=center|39\n|-\n!{{Escyr|2015}}\n|[[Leonor Andrade]]\n|Portuguese\n|\"[[H\u00e1 um mar que nos separa]]\"\n|align=center|14\n|align=center|19\n|-\n|{{N/A|{{Escyr|2016}}}}\n|colspan=\"7\" {{N/A|Did not participate}}\n|-bgcolor=\"gold\"\n!{{Escyr|2017}}\n|[[Salvador Sobral]]\n|Portuguese\n|\"[[Amar pelos dois]]\"\n|align=center|1\n|align=center|758\n|align=center|1\n|align=center|370\n|-bgcolor=\"#fe8080\"\n!{{Escyr|2018}}\n|[[Cl\u00e1udia Pascoal]]\n|Portuguese\n|\"[[O jardim]]\"\n|align=center|26 \u25c1\n|align=center|39\n|colspan=\"2\" data-sort-value=\"-9999\" {{N/A|Host country}}{{efn|name=note3|If a country had won the previous year, they did not have to compete in the semi-finals the following year.}}\n|-\n!{{Escyr|2019}}\n|[