ation\n! Venue\n! Presenters\n!Image\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|2018}}\n| [[Lisbon]]\n| [[Altice Arena]]\n| [[Catarina Furtado]], [[Daniela Ruah]], [[Filomena Cautela]] and [[S\u00edlvia Alberto]]\n|[[File:Eurovision 2018 Hosts 03.jpg|200px]]\n|-\n|}\n\n==Awards==\n===Marcel Bezen\u00e7on Awards===\n{{further|Marcel Bezen\u00e7on Awards}}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"font-size: 95%\"\n|-\n!Year\n!Category\n!Song\n!Composer\n!Performer\n!style=\"width:45px;\"|Final\n!style=\"width:45px;\"|Points\n!Host city\n!class=\"unsortable\"|{{Abbr|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| {{escyr|2008}}\n|Press Award\n| \"[[Senhora do mar (Negras \u00e1guas)]]\"\n|[[Andrej Babi\u0107]], Carlos Coelho\n| [[V\u00e2nia Fernandes]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"| 13\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"| 69\n|{{flagicon|Serbia|2004}} [[Belgrade]]\n|{{center|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://esctoday.com/12019/the_2008_bezenon_awards_winners/|title=The 2008 Bezen\u00e7on Awards winners|website=esctoday.com|date=27 May 2008|accessdate=8 December 2019|first=Stella|last=Floras}}</ref>}}\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"2\"| {{escyr|2017}}\n|Artistic Award{{Efn|Voted by commentators.}}\n|rowspan=\"2\"| \"[[Amar pelos dois]]\"\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[Lu\u00edsa Sobral]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"| [[Salvador Sobral]]\n|rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1\n|rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| 758\n|rowspan=\"2\"|{{flagicon|Ukraine}} [[Kiev]]\n|{{center|<ref name=\"mba 2017\">{{cite web|url=https://eurovision.tv/story/winners-of-the-marcel-bezencon-awards-2017-1|title=Winners of the Marcel Bezen\u00e7on Awards 2017|website=eurovision.tv|date=14 May 2017|accessdate=8 December 2019}}</ref>}}\n|-\n|Composer Award\n|{{center|<ref name=\"mba 2017\"/>}}\n|}\n\n===Barbara Dex Award===\n{{further|Barbara Dex Award}}\n{|class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"font-size:95%;\"\n!Year\n!Performer\n!Host city\n!{{abbr|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|{{Escyr|2006}}\n|[[Nonstop (band)|